name: r-contrast
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.24.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-contrast
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/contrast_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/contrast/contrast_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 589103633eb9d5958152189f52ba04bbe055376e31bfdf6f597f788aee612984

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-nlme
    - r-rms
    - r-sandwich
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-nlme
    - r-rms
    - r-sandwich

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('contrast')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('contrast')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/topepo/contrast
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: One degree of freedom contrasts for 'lm', 'glm', 'gls', and 'geese' objects.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
